test_bridgeERC721To_localTokenZeroAddres.details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge reverts for non externally owned accounts      when sending to a different address than the owner.

test_bridgeERC721To_remoteTokenZeroAddre.details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge reverts for a zero address remote token      when sending to a different address than the owner.

test_bridgeERC721To_succeeds().details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge successfully sends a token      to a different address than the owner.

test_bridgeERC721To_wrongOwner_reverts().details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge reverts for an incorrect owner

test_bridgeERC721_succeeds().details: Tests that the ERC721 can be bridged successfully.

test_bridgeERC721_wrongOwner_reverts().details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge reverts for an incorrect owner.

test_finalizeBridgeERC721_notEscrowed_re.details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge finalize reverts when the remote token      is not escrowed in the L1 bridge.

test_finalizeBridgeERC721_notFromRemoteM.details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge finalize reverts when not called      from the remote messenger.

test_finalizeBridgeERC721_notViaLocalMes.details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge finalize reverts when not called      by the remote bridge.

test_finalizeBridgeERC721_selfToken_reve.details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge finalize reverts when the local token      is set as the bridge itself.

test_finalizeBridgeERC721_succeeds().details: Tests that the ERC721 bridge successfully finalizes a withdrawal.

test_initialize_succeeds().details: Tests that the proxy is initialized with the correct values.
